**Services Page Outline**

Below is a starting point for your **Services** page that matches the look-and-feel of your homepage. It reuses your header and footer, then adds a hero section and a detailed services listing.

---

```html
<!-- services.html -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
<head>
  <meta charset='UTF-8' />
  <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
  <title>JZ Digital | Services</title>
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='css/styles.css' />
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css' />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Reuse header -->
  <header class='header'>
    <div class='header-content'>
      <div class='brand'>
        <img src='images/logo.jpg' alt='JZ Digital Logo' />
      </div>
<nav class="nav-inline">
  <a href="index.html"       >Home</a>
  <a href="services.html" class="active">Services</a>
  <a href="about.html"       >About</a>
  <a href="contact.html"     >Contact</a>
</nav>

    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Services Hero -->
  <section class='page-hero services-hero'>
    <div class='container'>
      <h1>Our Services</h1>
      <p>Discover how JZ Digital helps you automate smarter, work leaner, and grow faster.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Detailed Services List -->
  <main class='services-list container'>
    <!-- Service 1 -->
    <div class='service-item'>
      <i class='fas fa-network-wired service-icon'></i>
      <h3>Custom CRM Integration</h3>
      <p>
        We design and implement CRM systems tailored to your processes—ensuring
        seamless data flow, custom reporting, and a single source of truth for your client relationships.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 2 -->
    <div class='service-item'>
      <i class='fas fa-file-alt service-icon'></i>
      <h3>Document Automation</h3>
      <p>
        Automate document generation, approvals, and storage with workflows that reduce errors,
        save time, and keep your teams focused on high-value work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 3 -->
    <div class='service-item'>
      <i class='fas fa-cogs service-icon'></i>
      <h3>Workflow Automation</h3>
      <p>
        Streamline repetitive business processes—from notifications to task
        assignments—using custom scripts and integrations that scale with your growth.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 4 -->
    <div class='service-item'>
      <i class='fas fa-shield-alt service-icon'></i>
      <h3>Compliance & Security</h3>
      <p>
        Ensure ISO 27001, GDPR, and audit readiness with embedded compliance checks,
        encryption, and secure access controls across every layer of your solution.
