---

**Next Steps:**

1. Add CSS rules for `.services-hero`, `.services-list`, `.service-item`, and `.cta-section` in your `styles.css` to match your branding and layout (grid or flex).
2. Link your navigation so the active page is highlighted.
3. Replace placeholder icons or text as needed, and adjust copy to match your actual offerings.

Let me know which styling approach you prefer (grid vs flex), and I can generate the accompanying CSS snippets!


